originalText.text: Dr. Nehal made me feel so comfortable during my procedure. She explained everything to me in detail, made sure I understood all the information and that all my questions were answered. The nurses and staff were all so supportive, kind, and compassionate. I had such a great experience and highly recommend dr. Nehal.

originalText.text: I've been to Dr. Nehal for two separate MOHS procedures in the past few years.  Dr. Nehal is awesome in that she keeps you thoroughly informed and her staff are very attentive as well.  Facility is start of the art and cleanliness is top notch.  Best part is that Dr. Nehal does the procedure and then you are taken directly to plastic surgery to finish the procedure - all the same day!  This is awesome.  Thanks Dr. Nehal!!

originalText.text: Dr Nehal...what can I say.   I am just so grateful  Dr. Kahlil recommended her for my Mohs surgery.  She explained everything. I was so at ease.
